metadata.name: Not Nakamoto - The Power of Memes
metadata.created_by: found myself in a square pixel
metadata.description:
The Power of Memes - A man named Satoshi Nakamoto stated in an interview in 2014 not to be Satoshi Nakamoto  "I have nothing to do with Bitcoin."

This piece pays tribute to one of the strongest memes in crypto space and remixing "SeizeJPGs" & "NakamotoFreedom" by punk6529 & 6529er.


Seize the memes of production!

This piece is under public domain. Feel free to use it as you want.
